      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Main program                                              *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       main-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test su tipo operazione                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Start                                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        f-ope                =    "ST"
                     perform str-000      thru str-999
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Read record per chiave primaria             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           else if   f-ope                =    "RD"
                     perform rea-000      thru rea-999
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Read next                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           else if   f-ope                =    "RN"
                     perform nxt-000      thru nxt-999
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Get Record per chiave primaria              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           else if   f-ope                =    "GT"
                     perform rea-000      thru rea-999
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Get next                                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           else if   f-ope                =    "GN"
                     perform nxt-000      thru nxt-999
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Release record                              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           else if   f-ope                =    "RL"
                     perform rel-000      thru rel-999
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Delete record                               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           else if   f-ope                =    "DE"
                     perform del-000      thru del-999
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Update record                               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           else if   f-ope                =    "UP"
                     perform upd-000      thru upd-999
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Put record                                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           else if   f-ope                =    "PT"
                     perform put-000      thru put-999
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Force put record                            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           else if   f-ope                =    "FP"
                     perform fpt-000      thru fpt-999
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Open                                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           else if   f-ope                =    "OP"
                     perform opn-000      thru opn-999
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Close                                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           else if   f-ope                =    "CL"
                     perform cls-000      thru cls-999
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Normalizzazione record logico               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           else if   f-ope                =    "NO"
                     perform nor-000
                        thru nor-999                                  .
       main-999.
           exit program.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Open                                                      *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       opn-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Richiamo del modulo di segreteria per la di-    *
      *              * chiarazione di inizio modulo oggetto            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "M+"                 to   s-ope                  .
           move      i-ide-pmo            to   s-pmo                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/msegrt"
                                         using s                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Richiamo modulo di "iofnum" per l'esecuzione    *
      *              * effettiva dell'operazione                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           call      "swd/xpg/fls/ioc/obj/iofnum"
                                         using f
                                               rf-num                 .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Determinazione del numero di frammenti di 80    *
      *              * caratteri in cui deve essere suddiviso il re-   *
      *              * cord logico                                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      1                    to   z-inx                  .
       opn-200.
           move      z-inx                to   z-nfr                  .
           perform   uns-000              thru uns-999                .
           if        z-inx                not  = z-nfr 
                     go to opn-200.
           add       78                   to   z-nfr                  .
           divide    80                   into z-nfr                  .
       opn-999.
           exit.
           
